### TaskFlow Pro - REST Client API Requests
### VS Code REST Client Extension

### ─── Variables ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1
@contentType = application/json
# After login, manually set this:
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@refreshToken = YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE
@projectId = YOUR_PROJECT_ID_HERE
@taskId = YOUR_TASK_ID_HERE

### ─── 1. Register New User ────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "fullName": "Jane Smith",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "TestPass123!"
}

### ─── 2. Login ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "password": "TestPass123!"
}

### ─── 3. Refresh Token ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### ─── 4. Get My Profile ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

### ─── 5. Create Project ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "My First Project",
  "description": "A test project created via REST client",
  "visibility": "PRIVATE",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### ─── 6. Get All Projects ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects?page=0&size=10&status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

### ─── 7. Get Project by ID ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── 8. Create Task ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Implement login page",
  "description": "Create a responsive login form with validation",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "status": "TODO",
  "dueDate": "2025-12-31",
  "tags": ["frontend", "auth"]
}

### ─── 9. Get Tasks in Project ──────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/tasks?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── 10. Get Task by ID ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── 11. Update Task Status ──────────────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### ─── 12. Update Task Details ─────────────────────────────────────────────
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Updated task title",
  "priority": "CRITICAL",
  "description": "Updated description with more details"
}

### ─── 13. Add Comment to Task ─────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "content": "Working on this now! Will have a PR ready by EOD."
}

### ─── 14. Get Comments ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── 15. Get Notifications ───────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications?page=0&size=20&isRead=false
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── 16. Mark All Notifications Read ─────────────────────────────────────
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── 17. Get Project Activity ─────────────────────────────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/activities?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── 18. Add Member to Project ────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/projects/{{projectId}}/members
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "developer@example.com",
  "role": "MEMBER"
}

### ─── 19. Delete Task ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── 20. Logout ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}
